{"type":"text","timestamp":1783411863715,"sessionID":"ses_0c45efdf6ffeLkJl10898xKnRC","part":{"id":"prt_f3ba16cbe001OfHHrGC2pR2bm8","messageID":"msg_f3ba16754001YoqJrmGzfMNUPx","sessionID":"ses_0c45efdf6ffeLkJl10898xKnRC","type":"text","text":"```json\n{\n  \"anomaly_ids\": [],\n  \"answer\": \"2025年现行有效审批线规定：单笔费用报销金额大于等于10000元且小于50000元的，应提交部门总经理审批。旧版（2022版）曾规定8000元即需部门总经理审批，但该版已废止。现行审批权限依据《XX证券授权管理办法》附件二执行。\",\n  \"citations\": [\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"03_authorization_management.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"附件二\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"doc_id\": \"01_expense_reimbursement_2025.md\",\n      \"clause_no\": \"第五条\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```","time":{"start":1783411862718,"end":1783411863652}}}
